text: Jordan Mageo (born January 6, 1997) is an American Samoan sprinter. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 100 metres race; her time of 13.72 seconds in the preliminary round did not qualify her for the first round. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:American people of Samoan descent Category:American Samoan female sprinters Category:Olympic track and field athletes of American Samoa Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics
